{
    "poem_title": "LAON",
    "author": "Albert Glatigny",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1870",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Il est des villes qui sont fières",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "De se changer en cimetières",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Plutôt que de voir outrager",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Leurs foyers, leurs maisons, leurs rues,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Et leurs morts, ombres apparues",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Terribles devant l'étranger !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il est des villes qui sont fières\nDe se changer en cimetières\nPlutôt que de voir outrager\nLeurs foyers, leurs maisons, leurs rues,\nEt leurs morts, ombres apparues\nTerribles devant l'étranger !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Elles n'ont qu'un mot : résistance !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Elles donnent leur existence",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Stoïquement et gravement ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "La grande âme de la patrie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Vit dans leur enceinte inflétrie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Et chante sur le sol fumant.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Elles n'ont qu'un mot : résistance !\nElles donnent leur existence\nStoïquement et gravement ;\nLa grande âme de la patrie\nVit dans leur enceinte inflétrie,\nEt chante sur le sol fumant."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "C'est Strasbourg calme sous les bombes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Qui chaque jour ouvrant des tombes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Passent foudroyantes dans l'air ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Noble cité qui se résigne",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "À la mort, et veut rester digne",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "De ses fils, Ulrich et Kléber !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est Strasbourg calme sous les bombes\nQui chaque jour ouvrant des tombes,\nPassent foudroyantes dans l'air ;\nNoble cité qui se résigne\nÀ la mort, et veut rester digne\nDe ses fils, Ulrich et Kléber !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "C'est Toul, c'est Phalsbourg et Mézières",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Qu'entourent de rouges lisières",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Faites de mitraille et d'obus ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "C'est Montmédy, c'est Metz qui raille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Du haut de sa forte muraille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Les prussiens déjà fourbus.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est Toul, c'est Phalsbourg et Mézières\nQu'entourent de rouges lisières\nFaites de mitraille et d'obus ;\nC'est Montmédy, c'est Metz qui raille,\nDu haut de sa forte muraille,\nLes prussiens déjà fourbus."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Elles veulent bien disparaître,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Mais non pas laisser un nom traître.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Elles sont hautaines. Leur front",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Indomptable auquel l'atmosphère",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Fait une couronne, préfère",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Les cicatrices à l'affront.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Elles veulent bien disparaître,\nMais non pas laisser un nom traître.\nElles sont hautaines. Leur front\nIndomptable auquel l'atmosphère\nFait une couronne, préfère\nLes cicatrices à l'affront."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Elles sont l'honneur et l'exemple",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "De l'univers qui les contemple.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Leur sang, qu'il est pur et vermeil !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Coule par de noires blessures,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Mais leur joue est sans flétrissures,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Mais leurs yeux sont pleins de soleil.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Elles sont l'honneur et l'exemple\nDe l'univers qui les contemple.\nLeur sang, qu'il est pur et vermeil !\nCoule par de noires blessures,\nMais leur joue est sans flétrissures,\nMais leurs yeux sont pleins de soleil."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Elles protégent, ces pucelles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "La terre sacrée, entre celles",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Dont le nom veut dire grandeur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Aux loups du nord, pleins de cyniques",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Appétits, leurs blanches tuniques",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Imposent encor la pudeur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Elles protégent, ces pucelles,\nLa terre sacrée, entre celles\nDont le nom veut dire grandeur.\nAux loups du nord, pleins de cyniques\nAppétits, leurs blanches tuniques\nImposent encor la pudeur."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Ô villes saintes, ô martyres !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Vous dont les suaves sourires",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Font baisser les yeux aux bourreaux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Oh ! Quel pieux pèlerinage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Le monde fera, d'âge en âge,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Chez vous, nourrices de héros !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ô villes saintes, ô martyres !\nVous dont les suaves sourires\nFont baisser les yeux aux bourreaux,\nOh ! Quel pieux pèlerinage\nLe monde fera, d'âge en âge,\nChez vous, nourrices de héros !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Mais à côté de ces guerrières,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Il est d'autres villes moins fières,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Bourgeoises dont l'unique plan",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Est de vivre en paix dans la honte,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Et de lécher la main qui dompte :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "N'est-ce pas, ô cité de Laon ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais à côté de ces guerrières,\nIl est d'autres villes moins fières,\nBourgeoises dont l'unique plan\nEst de vivre en paix dans la honte,\nEt de lécher la main qui dompte :\nN'est-ce pas, ô cité de Laon ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Bah ! Que t'importe l'infamie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Pourvu qu'on te laisse endormie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Dans ton égoïsme ouaté !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "La gloire, quelquefois, ça coûte,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Et c'est du sang qu'il en dégoutte ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "C'est pénible, la liberté.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Bah ! Que t'importe l'infamie,\nPourvu qu'on te laisse endormie\nDans ton égoïsme ouaté !\nLa gloire, quelquefois, ça coûte,\nEt c'est du sang qu'il en dégoutte ;\nC'est pénible, la liberté."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Pourquoi ne pas vivre à son aise,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Loin du bruit et de la fournaise ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "À quoi bon se brûler au feu ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "L'ennemi n'est pas si farouche ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Il veut s'étendre dans ta couche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Pourquoi l'en empêcher, bon dieu !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pourquoi ne pas vivre à son aise,\nLoin du bruit et de la fournaise ?\nÀ quoi bon se brûler au feu ?\nL'ennemi n'est pas si farouche ;\nIl veut s'étendre dans ta couche,\nPourquoi l'en empêcher, bon dieu !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Laon est une fille publique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Qui veut bien rire, et ne s'explique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Nul de ces refus violents",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Que d'autres villes font entendre.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Enfin, puisqu'elle veut bien tendre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Sa lèvre aux baisers des uhlans !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Laon est une fille publique\nQui veut bien rire, et ne s'explique\nNul de ces refus violents\nQue d'autres villes font entendre.\nEnfin, puisqu'elle veut bien tendre\nSa lèvre aux baisers des uhlans !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Ça l'irrite qu'on la défende,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "Cette catin ; elle appréhende",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Les gros mots de son prussien.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Il pourrait la battre. Eh ! Qu'a-t-elle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Donc à risquer ? Sa fange est telle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Qu'elle n'a plus d'honneur ancien.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ça l'irrite qu'on la défende,\nCette catin ; elle appréhende\nLes gros mots de son prussien.\nIl pourrait la battre. Eh ! Qu'a-t-elle\nDonc à risquer ? Sa fange est telle,\nQu'elle n'a plus d'honneur ancien."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 14,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Ville prudente, ville infâme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Ah ! Ville sans cœur et sans âme !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "J'espère qu'on va te rayer",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 82,
                    "line_text": "Du nombre des cités de France ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 83,
                    "line_text": "Puisque tu mens à l'espérance,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 84,
                    "line_text": "Que tu ne sais que t'effrayer,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ville prudente, ville infâme,\nAh ! Ville sans cœur et sans âme !\nJ'espère qu'on va te rayer\nDu nombre des cités de France ;\nPuisque tu mens à l'espérance,\nQue tu ne sais que t'effrayer,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 15,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 85,
                    "line_text": "Que ta citadelle écroulée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 86,
                    "line_text": "Atteste, sombre et désolée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 87,
                    "line_text": "Qu'au moins un français était là,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 88,
                    "line_text": "Qui n'acceptant point ta défaite,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
